// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1298 — Mass File Rename (ransomhub)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5f44052f-69ad-5a16-aa08-b80874cb7761

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
